{"tid":473291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何不食肉糜:羅致光反問貧窮長者何不拿綜援","createTime":"2017-11-19T06:00:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T13:40:55.000Z","uid":36901,"like":52,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"2e0fec427d49b587384fa3efc009032bb3ad29ca","tid":473291,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:00:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5a110ff1e60383f32d780a5a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5a110ff1e60383f32d780a5a&d=xUcJZgEr%2B061WxnRHYnldIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=0774b9c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5a110ff1e60383f32d780a5a</a><br />\n<br />\n真係離地萬仗<br />\n現你老味現行政策係一拿綜援要成家一齊拿的<br />\n政府係咪鼓勵市民全家拿綜援<br />\n定係鼓勵將老人丟入老人院等政府養?<br />\n真係食撚屎<br />\n<br />\n死撚左去啦垃圾羅致光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c879d853bff6173a9b868f8c83e21a1eafa2760","tid":473291,"uid":71237,"like":21,"dislike":2,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:02:26.000Z","msg":"全家拎綜援有咩問題?"},{"pid":"de57de9bdb446d84c5e735a38860b840afe590a9","tid":473291,"uid":22858,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五毛係咪好驚下個到你就無糧出</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<del><span style=\"color: red;\">三色貓</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">法國佬巫斯義</span></del>、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">極右派政治家</span></del>、民國復興、群龍共舞、優美開始、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Coffee@</span></del>、JR、RedBaron = Epiphany、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">Gladiclus</span></del>、D_Wade、dewi、<del><span style=\"color: red;\">newlife</span></del>、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東</span></strong>"},{"pid":"f77b127c31bd06a5b13f396c1aeca9502a1c9d2a","tid":473291,"uid":36901,"like":54,"dislike":2,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:15:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全家拎綜援有咩問題?</blockquote><br />\n舉個例<br />\n一家四個人<br />\n仔,老豆,老母,阿婆<br />\n阿婆要長期照顧,使費甚巨<br />\n老豆有小小退休金,緊夠自己基本生活<br />\n老母打分基層工<br />\n仔剛出黎社會做野<br />\n<br />\n呢個case得阿婆,老豆係進入貧窮線<br />\n現行政策佢地唔可以單獨拿綜援<br />\n一拿就要個仔同老母都唔撚做野一齊拿<br />\n社署亦唔可能批你d case<br />\n<br />\n咁唯一方法就係趕老豆同阿婆去老人院等政府養<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知羅致光係乜logic<br />\n一面叫人居家安老<br />\n一面叫人拿綜援<br />\n但又唔俾有需要個案獨立申請<br />\n要陷家拿<br />\n結果咪又係迫d仔女趕晒d老人入老人院<br />\n跟住安老宿位又爆煲<br />\n成個問題越搞越嚴重<br />\n呢個真係弱智政府"},{"pid":"ee66d3f67ec062c5608f0d6902487ef1fa9e20ca","tid":473291,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:17:49.000Z","msg":"邊個話要全家拎"},{"pid":"a07b86f30f4cf8acf81fb8062a505e9ce15bd601","tid":473291,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:19:00.000Z","msg":"有綜援就冇長者生活津貼。只可2選1"},{"pid":"3b6613a119634ae278197f90ca96020c23ae1af9","tid":473291,"uid":6297,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:21:46.000Z","msg":"公屋長者拎綜緩同住子女要簽衰仔紙，公屋要除名"},{"pid":"793bcb412114cd42d798cb29d9d4f68f4134d14a","tid":473291,"uid":36901,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊個話要全家拎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/FAQ/019001/index.shtm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.1823.gov.hk%2Fbig5%2FFAQ%2F019001%2Findex.shtm&d=xUcJZgEr%2B061WxnRHYnldIzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e710c82c\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.1823.gov.hk/big5/FAQ/019001/index.shtm</a><br />\n申請人必須通過資產及入息的審查。<span style=\"color: red;\">申請人如與家人同住，便須以家庭為單位提出申請</span>。在決定一個家庭是否符合資格領取綜援時，社署會考慮整個家庭的資源和需要。換言之，社署會把所有家庭成員的每月收入和所需開支一併計算。"},{"pid":"74c5a354c32ea2252971b3f172e620528f9e1933","tid":473291,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有綜援就冇長者生活津貼。只可2選1</blockquote><br />\n長生津唔到候唔到肺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e640bc599db62dee941177c59bd11f6df048597","tid":473291,"uid":34103,"like":4,"dislike":23,"score":-19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:09:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4bafcab22151c088aca6ddd8a37e1794bbc36c2a","tid":473291,"uid":36901,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:10:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>政府都算係咁<br />\n班低收入家庭做左幾廿年人完全冇交過稅，退休後都有得拎津貼</blockquote><br />\n你食屎啦"},{"pid":"94bc3939f7c8f275645aec22cf5a0811e26b9d17","tid":473291,"uid":34103,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:22:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecc4fbdb436f1f09789d951be7c6d869d556e463","tid":473291,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:23:24.000Z","msg":"長者攞綜援，除咗會被標籤化外，脫離綜援網亦好難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c026a9b52514001cd84f4c7c1b48fef89346a22","tid":473291,"uid":36901,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>政府都算係咁<br />\n班低收入家庭做左幾廿年人完全冇交過稅，退休後都有