 />\n贏左即時退休<br />\n輸左就謹遵羅致光教晦下半世食老綜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至叻係你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">聽朝記得準時返工喎</span>"},{"pid":"54fc7a42eda984ee8b98dc80dee2656ae43d41d5","tid":473291,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己老母自己養💁🏻&zwj;♂️</blockquote><br />\n乜係自己老母養自己咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fa94ee70d3fd1ad7837467baa84d69e8d80f42","tid":473291,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T09:35:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己老母自己養💁🏻&zwj;♂️</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n乜唔係自己老母養自己咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}